org.wso2.carbon.identity.oauth2.authcontext

Interface ClaimsRetriever

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultClaimsRetriever

    public interface ClaimsRetriever
    This interface encapsulates a user claims retriever. The retrieved claims are encoded to the token during subscriber validation in the order defined by the SortedMap. Anyone trying to add custom user properties to the token should implement this interface and mention the fully qualified class name in identity.xml -> OAuth -> TokenGeneration -> ClaimsRetrieverImplClass
